Functional requirements

The system must allow user to create a new task.
The system must ask the estimated time to be the task done.
The system must assign a number of pomodoros depending the estimated time.
The system must allow the user to start and cancel the pomodoro.
The system must set a timer once the pomodoro is started.
The system must notify user and check the pomodor once the time is finished.
The system must set a 5 minutes rest timer after each pomodoro.
The system must set a 15 minutes rest timer after 4 pomodoros.
The system must allow the user change the timers duration

Non-Functional Requirements

The system should be developed in python.
The system should be a web porject
